@startuml e2e-09-kb-add-topic
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
title E2E-09: Add New KB Topic and Incremental Index

actor User
participant "CLI\nmain.py" as CLI
participant "Indexer\nindexer.py" as IDX
participant "Manifest\nmanifest.json" as MAN
participant "chunker_fn\nchunker.py" as CHK
participant "ContextCache\ncontext_cache.json" as CC
participant "EmbedFn\n(embedder.py)" as EMB
participant "VectorStore\n(ChromaDB)" as VS

== Step 1: Add the file ==

User -> CLI : python cli/main.py kb add new-topic.md
CLI -> CLI : validate: suffix == ".md"

alt file already exists in kb/
  CLI --> User : "File already exists. Overwrite? [y/N]"
  User -> CLI : y
end

CLI -> CLI : shutil.copy2(src, kb/new-topic.md)
CLI --> User : "Added kb/new-topic.md.\n  Run 'python cli/main.py kb index' to index it."

note over User, VS : kb list now shows new-topic.md as "not yet indexed ⚠"

== Step 2: List KB status (optional verification) ==

User -> CLI : python cli/main.py kb list
CLI -> MAN : read manifest.json
MAN --> CLI : {indexed_files: [existing-files...]}
CLI --> User : File                    Indexed   Chunks   Last Modified\n──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nexisting-topic.md       yes       12       2026-04-10\nnew-topic.md            no        —        2026-04-19  ⚠

== Step 3: Incremental index ==

User -> CLI : python cli/main.py kb index
CLI -> IDX : build_incremental()

IDX -> MAN : diff(kb_dir)
note right : Compares current mtime of each .md\nagainst manifest.json snapshot
MAN --> IDX : FileDiff(\n  new=["new-topic.md"],\n  changed=[],\n  deleted=[]  )

loop for each file in diff.new + diff.changed
  note over IDX : diff.deleted files: delete_by_source() then skip
  IDX -> IDX : delete_by_source(path) [for changed files]
  IDX -> CHK : chunk_markdown(file_text, source_file)
  CHK --> IDX : [Chunk(heading="Section A", text="...", source_file="new-topic.md"), ...]

  loop for each Chunk
    IDX -> CC : get(chunk_hash(chunk.text))

    alt cache MISS
      note right : context_adapter=None in basic mode\n— skip model context call
      IDX -> IDX : prepared = chunk.text
    else cache HIT (only relevant if context_adapter set)
      CC --> IDX : cached_context_string
      IDX -> IDX : prepared = "{ctx}\n\n{chunk.text}"
    end

    IDX -> EMB : encode(prepared)
    EMB --> IDX : vector[N]
    IDX -> VS : add([chunk_id], [vector],\n        [chunk.text], [{source_file, heading}])
  end

  IDX -> MAN : update(path)
end

IDX -> CC : save()
CLI --> User : "Incremental index update complete."

== Verification ==

User -> CLI : python cli/main.py kb list
CLI --> User : File                    Indexed   Chunks   Last Modified\n──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nexisting-topic.md       yes       12       2026-04-10\nnew-topic.md            yes       4        2026-04-19

User -> CLI : python cli/main.py kb search "new topic keywords" --top 3
CLI --> User : [1] new-topic.md — Section A\n    <excerpt>...\n[2] ...

@enduml
